        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　願共諸眾生　　往生華藏海　　極樂淨土中次法界菩提道場中執金剛神眾南無得見如來示現無邊色相身解脫門妙色那羅延執金剛神南無得佛身一一毛如日輪現種種光明雲解脫門日輪速疾幢執金剛神南無得化現無量身大神變解脫門須彌華光執金剛神南無得無邊隨類音解脫門清淨雲音執金剛神南無得現為一切世間主開悟眾生解脫門妙臂天主執金剛神南無得普開示一切佛法差別門咸盡無遺解脫門可愛樂光明執金剛神南無得以可愛樂莊嚴具攝一切樹神解脫門大樹雷音執金剛神南無得如來廣大福莊嚴聚皆具足明了解脫門師子王光明執金剛神南無得普觀察險惡眾生心為現威嚴身解脫門密燄吉祥目執金剛神南無得普雨一切菩薩莊嚴具摩尼髻解脫門蓮華摩尼髻執金剛神南無如是等而為上首。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0177b01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其數無量。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0177b22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切執金剛神。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0177b22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　十方盡歸命　　滅罪增淨信　　願生華藏海　極樂淨土中經云。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0177b23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復次普賢菩薩(至)盡與如來平等法。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0177c01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　願共諸眾生　　往生華藏海　　極樂淨土中南無入不思議境界種種解脫門普賢菩薩摩訶薩　十方盡歸命　　滅罪增淨信　　願生華藏海　極樂淨土中經云。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0177c02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復次淨德妙光菩薩(至)一切苦難皆消滅。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0177c06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　願共諸眾生　　往生華藏海　　極樂淨土中次法界菩提道場中如來師子之座一切菩薩海眾南無得徧往十方菩薩眾會莊嚴道場解脫門淨德妙光菩薩摩訶薩南無得一念中現無盡成正覺門教化成熟不思議眾生界解脫門普得最勝鐙光照菩薩摩訶薩南無得修習菩薩福德莊嚴出生一切佛國土解脫門普光師子幢菩薩摩訶薩南無得觀察佛神通境界無迷惑解脫門普寶燄妙光菩薩摩訶薩南無得於一眾會道場中示現一切佛土莊嚴解脫門普音功德海幢菩薩摩訶薩南無得隨逐如來觀察甚深廣大法界藏解脫門普智光照如來境菩薩摩訶薩南無得親近承事一切諸佛供養藏解脫門普覺悅意聲菩薩摩訶薩南無得出生一切神變廣大加持解脫門普清淨無盡福威光菩薩摩訶薩南無得普入一切世間行出生菩薩無邊行門解脫門普寶髻華幢菩薩摩訶薩南無得能於無相法界中出現一切諸佛境界解脫門普相最勝光菩薩摩訶薩南無如是等而為上首。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0177c07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其數無量。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0178a06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切菩薩。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0178a06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　十方盡歸命　　滅罪增淨信　　願生華藏海　極樂淨土中經云。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0178a07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復次海月光大明菩薩(至)一切國土皆明顯。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0178a09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　願共諸眾生　　往生華藏海　　極樂淨土中　　　次法界菩提道場中如來師子之座一切菩薩海眾南無得出生菩薩諸地諸波羅蜜教化眾生及嚴淨一切佛國土方便解脫門海月光大明菩薩摩訶薩南無得念念中普入法界種種差別處解脫門雲音海光離垢藏菩薩摩訶薩南無得不可思議劫於一切眾生前現清淨大功德解脫門智生寶髻菩薩摩訶薩南無得普見十方一切菩薩初詣道場時種種莊嚴解脫門功德自在王淨光菩薩摩訶薩南無得隨諸眾生根解海普為顯示一切佛法解脫門善勇猛蓮華髻菩薩摩訶薩南無得成就如來智永住無量劫解脫門普智雲日幢菩薩摩訶薩南無得普入一切無邊法印力解脫門大精進金剛臍菩薩摩訶薩南無得顯示現在一切佛始修菩薩行乃至成就智慧聚解脫門香燄光幢菩薩摩訶薩南無得安住毗盧遮那一切大願海解脫門大明德深美音菩薩摩訶薩南無得顯示如來徧法界甚深境界解脫門大福光智生菩薩摩訶薩南無如是等而為上首。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0178a10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其數無量。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0178b10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切菩薩。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0178b10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　十方盡歸命　　滅罪增淨信　　願生華藏海　極樂淨土中經云。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0178b11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時如來師子之座(至)以佛力故能宣說。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0178b13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　願共諸眾生　　往生華藏海　　極樂淨土中次法界菩提道場中如來師子之座輪臺基陛及諸戶牗所出一切海眾南無法界菩提道場如來師子之座眾寶妙華輪臺基陛及諸戶牖如是一切莊嚴具中佛剎微塵數一切菩薩海眾南無海慧自在神通王菩薩摩訶薩南無雷音普震菩薩摩訶薩南無眾寶光明髻菩薩摩訶薩南無大智日勇猛慧菩薩摩訶薩南無不思議功德寶智印菩薩摩訶薩南無百目蓮華髻菩薩摩訶薩南無金燄圓滿光菩薩摩訶薩南無法界普音菩薩摩訶薩南無雲音淨月菩薩摩訶薩南無善勇猛光幢菩薩摩訶薩南無如是等不可說不可說佛剎極微塵數同出現一切菩薩海眾至心歸命。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0178b14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "禮大方廣佛華嚴經華藏世界海本尊毗盧遮那佛　十方盡歸命　　滅罪增淨信　　願生華藏海　極樂淨土中次華藏世界莊嚴海世主會○天地現瑞經云。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0178c08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時華藏莊嚴世界海(至)世界海中悉亦如是。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0178c13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　願共諸眾生　　往生華藏海　　極樂淨土中南無娑婆世界道場眾中雨眾雲具各入如來解脫門一切諸世主南無華藏莊嚴世界海中一切國內皆亦如是一切世主南無如是等不可說佛剎微塵數華藏世界一切剎海皆亦如是一切世主至心歸命。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0178c14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "禮大方廣佛華嚴經華藏世界海本尊毗盧遮那佛　十方盡歸命　　滅罪增淨信　　願生華藏海　極樂淨土中次妄語罪懺悔惟願帝網無盡佛法僧寶。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0178c21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "毗盧遮那如來。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "普賢文殊海會聖眾。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a02_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世出世神。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慈悲本願。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "放大光明。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a03_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "炤於法會。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "證盟護念。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "哀愍攝受。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願我及一切眾生海。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自從無始。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "直至今時。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "業海無盡。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "帝網重重。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切妄語罪業。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "發露懺悔。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a05_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夫妄語罪者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "苗輕根重。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "損害極多。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是業道罪。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及違戒律。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "破菩薩戒。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "犯波羅夷。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或性或遮悉皆結重。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "智度論云。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a08_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妄語者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不淨心欲誑他覆隱實。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a09_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "出異論生口業。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a09_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是名妄語。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a09_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妄語之罪。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從言聲相解生。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a10_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若不相解。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a10_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖不實語。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a10_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無妄語罪。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a11_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是妄語者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a11_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "知言不知。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a11_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知言知。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a11_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "見言不見。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a11_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不見言見。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a12_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聞言不聞。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a12_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不聞言聞。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a12_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是名妄語。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a12_25",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若不作。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a12_26",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是名不妄語。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妄語之人。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "先自誑身。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然後誑人。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以實為虗。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a13_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以虗為實。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "虗實顛倒。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不受善法。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a14_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如覆瓶。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a14_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "水不得入。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a14_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妄語之人。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a15_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心無慚愧。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a15_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "閉塞天道涅槃之門。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a15_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀知此罪。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故不作。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a16_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "問曰。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a16_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若妄語有如是罪。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a16_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故妄語。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a16_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "答曰。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a16_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有人愚癡少智。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "遭事苦厄。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a17_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妄語求脫。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a17_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知事發。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a17_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今世得罪。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a17_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知後世。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a18_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有大罪報。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a18_25",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有人雖知妄語罪。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a18_26",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慳貪瞋恚。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a18_27",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愚癡多故。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a19_28",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而作妄語。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a19_29",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有人雖不貪恚。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a19_30",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而妄證人罪。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a19_31",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心謂實爾。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a20_32",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "死墮地獄。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a20_33",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如佛說妄語有十罪。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a20_34",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a20_35",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a21_36",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "口氣常臭。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a21_37",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a21_38",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善神遠離。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a21_39",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非人得便。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a21_40",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a21_41",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖有實語。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a22_42",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "人不信受。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a22_43",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a22_44",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "智人謀議。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a22_45",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常不參與。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a22_46",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a22_47",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常被誹謗醜惡之聲。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a23_48",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "周聞天下。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a23_49",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a23_50",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "人所不敬。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a23_51",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖有教敕。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a23_52",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "人不信用。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a24_53",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a24_54",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常多憂愁。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a24_55",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a24_56",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "種誹謗業因緣。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179a24_57",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b01_58",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身壞命終。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b01_59",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當墮地獄。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b01_60",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b01_61",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若出為人。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b01_62",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常被誹謗。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b01_63",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是種種不作。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b02_64",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是為不妄語。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b02_65",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "名口善律儀。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b02_66",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我等為無明所覆。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不識妄語罪因。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今遇道場。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "方始覺知。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "歸命毗盧遮那如來。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及一切賢聖海眾。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "燒香散華。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妄語罪報。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "發露懺悔。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不敢覆藏。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以此因緣。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我及法界眾生海。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b05_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妄語重罪。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願皆清淨。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "次懺悔滅罪印呪",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唵薩栗末(二合)巴(引)巴眉悉普怛[口*捺]曷捺末日囉也莎曷(應誦三徧)　百劫積集罪　　一念悉盪除　　如火焚枯草　滅盡無有餘　我昔所造諸惡業　　皆由無始貪瞋癡　從身語意之所生　　一切我今皆懺悔懺悔已。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至心歸命。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "禮本尊毗盧遮那佛。",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "○(白)眾等聽說經中無常偈",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　無上諸世尊　　獨覺聲聞眾　　尚捨無常身　何況於凡夫　　父母及妻子　　兄弟并眷屬　目觀生死隔　　云何不愁歎　　是故勸諸人　諦聽真實法　　共捨無常處　　當行不死門　佛教如甘露　　除熱得清涼　　一心應善聽　能滅諸煩惱大方廣佛華嚴經海印道場十重行願常徧禮懺儀卷第七",
        "from": "X74n1470_007:0179b16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]